### Memory usage estimates for 8GB VRAM

| Operation | Estimated VRAM |
|-----------|---------------|
| Base model (4-bit Qwen 1.5B) | ~1.2 GB |
| LoRA adapters (r=16) | ~0.1 GB |
| Optimizer states (paged 8-bit) | ~0.4 GB |
| Activations + gradients (batch=2, seq=512, grad ckpt) | ~2.5 GB |
| CUDA overhead | ~0.5 GB |
| **Total SFT** | **~4.7 GB** ✅ |
| DPO simple (no ref model copy) | **~5.2 GB** ✅ |
| DPO full (with ref model) | **~7.5 GB** ⚠️ tight |

The simplified DPO script (`dpo_train_simple.py`) is recommended for 8GB cards because it uses PEFT's implicit reference instead of loading a second model.

